       P995-INSERT-ERROS.
      *- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - *

           MOVE   "BPCSPFIN2"    TO  ERRPRG OF KYCT900A.
           MOVE     WS-NURACI    TO  RACINE OF KYCT900A.

